rows.label: qst650408_msg0001
rows.name:
The three kids went to play
outside the village, and
they're all still not back...

rows.label: qst650408_msg0002
rows.name:
What's worse, my husband
went to look for them, and
now he's missing too...

rows.label: qst650408_msg0003
rows.name:
The little ones said they
were going in the direction
of Yeshiva Harbor.

rows.label: qst650408_msg0004
rows.name: Would you be so kind as to look...?

rows.label: qst650408_msg0101
rows.name:
So Raymon's safe and sound?
Oh, thank the stars...

rows.label: qst650408_msg0102
rows.name:
I hope the kids are, too...
Wherever they are...
